title: The Billy Taylor Trio: Cool Jazz with Jimmy Owens
tags: John F. Kennedy Center For The Performing Arts

description: Join legendary jazz pianist, composer and educator Dr. Billy Taylor and his trio (Chip Jackson on bass and Steve Johns on drums) with special guest trumpet/flugelhorn player Jimmy Owens as they explore the Cool style of jazz. The group performs jazz standards, including "Geneva's Move," "Boplicity," "Ladybird," "Half Nelson," "A Line For Lyons," "My Funny Valentine," and "Bernie's Tune" (recorded in 1999 at C. D. Hylton High School in Woodbridge, VA).
